<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٤١٧ - هـ ش ش]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هشَّشَ يهشِّش، تهشيشًا، فهو مُهشِّش، والمفعول مُهشَّش<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• هشَّش فلانًا:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - فرّحه ونشَّطه <span class="c1">"هشَّشه نجاحُه في العمل"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - استضعفَهُ <span class="c1">"هشَّش خصمَه فضربَه"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>